    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2004-11-19</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2004-12-06T20:43:46Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Energy Independence Act of 2004 - Amends the Department of Energy Organization Act to require the National Energy Policy Plan to include a strategic plan for U.S. energy self-sufficiency by the year 2015 which: (1) examines and reports on existing energy technology and domestic resources as well as developing energy generation and transmission technologies, focusing on the integration of fuel cell technology into an overall national energy portfolio to achieve energy self-sufficiency within ten years; and (2) recommend to Congress targeted research and development in promising new energy generation and transmission technologies, and funding levels to implement a plan for achieving such self-sufficiency.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
